    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Rubus micropetalus Gardner. A. Habitat; B. Inflorescence; C. Abaxial surface of leaves; D. Flower; E. Fruits; F & G. Stipules (showing adaxial and abaxial surface); H & I. Sepals (showing adaxial and abaxial surface); J. Petal; K & L. Bracts (showing adaxial and abaxial surface); M. Drupelet. (Photos: Bhavadas N)." ;
